OL,3,CNo bail but no life sentence either -
OL,4,Cwhat next for Sean 'Diddy' Combs?
OL,6,FIn sweltering Manhattan temperatures,
OL,7,Fit was hard to move an inch as we
OL,8,Fwaited with hundreds of journalists
OL,9,Fand TV crews for the judge's decision
OL,10,Fon whether or not to grant bail to
OL,11,FSean "Diddy" Combs.
OL,13,FAt just after 5pm Eastern Time, we
OL,14,Fwatched as the rapper's mother,
OL,15,Falongside six of his seven children,
OL,16,Fclimbed out of black people carrier
OL,17,Fand headed back into court.
