OL,3,CNo bail but no life sentence either -
OL,4,Cwhat next for Sean 'Diddy' Combs?
OL,6,FThey'd been smiling when they left a
OL,7,Ffew hours before, deeply relieved that
OL,8,FCombs' no longer faced the prospect of
OL,9,Fspending the rest of his life in
OL,10,Fprison. But having attended almost
OL,11,Fevery day of his seven week trial, now
OL,12,Fthey were back on tenterhooks,
OL,13,Fwondering if he was about to come home
OL,14,Fon bail after nearly ten months in
OL,15,Fprison.
