OL,3,CNo bail but no life sentence either -
OL,4,Cwhat next for Sean 'Diddy' Combs?
OL,6,FInside the court Combs, who earlier
OL,7,Fhad sunk to his knees as the jury
OL,8,Fcleared him of the most serious
OL,9,Fcharges, acknowledged them, looking
OL,10,Fcomposed as he waited for the judge's
OL,11,Fdecision. Outside, some fans still
OL,12,Fheld placards, urging the judge to
OL,13,F"Free Puff".
