OL,3,CNo bail but no life sentence either -
OL,4,Cwhat next for Sean 'Diddy' Combs?
OL,6,FPointing out that even his defence
OL,7,Fteam accepted he was a domestic abuser
OL,8,Fwith a history of violence, the
OL,9,Fprosecution also argued Combs would be
OL,10,Fa danger to the community unless he
OL,11,Fremained in custody.
OL,13,FThe judge agreed, refusing bail and
OL,14,Fconsigning the fallen rap idol to more
OL,15,Ftime behind bars with a provisional
OL,16,Fdate given of October 3 for his final
OL,17,Fsentence to be decided.
