OL,3,CNo bail but no life sentence either -
OL,4,Cwhat next for Sean 'Diddy' Combs?
OL,6,FThat didn't stop Combs' lawyer Marc
OL,7,FAgnifilo emerging from court to tell
OL,8,Fthe waiting crowd that today had been
OL,9,Fa "victory of all victories".
OL,11,FAfter weeks of sordid details that
OL,12,Fhave revealed the disturbing reality
OL,13,Fof parts of the music industry, that
OL,14,Ffelt a little jarring. But there is no
OL,15,Fdoubt that for the three-time Grammy
OL,16,Fwinning Combs, as deeply flawed as he
OL,17,Fis talented, today could have been
OL,18,Fmuch, much worse.
